OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO called to give
OL,4,Cevidence to MPs after Kent supply
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSouth East Water's CEO, David Hinton,
OL,8,Fhas been called to give evidence to
OL,9,FMPs after disruption to supplies in
OL,10,FKent.
OL,12,F24,000 homes in and around Tunbridge
OL,13,FWells have experienced a loss of water
OL,14,For low pressure since November 29.
OL,16,FCommunities continue to observe a boil
OL,17,Fwater notice prompting the EFRA
OL,18,FCommittee to organise a public
OL,19,Fevidence session in the new year.
