OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO called to give
OL,4,Cevidence to MPs after Kent supply
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Committee will hold the session on
OL,8,FJanuary 6, 2026 and has written to Mr
OL,9,FHinton to extend the invitation to
OL,10,Fattend.
OL,12,FThe Drinking Water Inspectorate will
OL,13,Falso be invited.
OL,15,FThe EFRA Chair, Alistair Carmichael MP
OL,16,Fwrote to the CEO of South East Water
OL,17,F(SEW) on 3 December, setting out his
OL,18,Fsignificant concerns about the lack of
OL,19,Faccess to water for residents and
OL,20,Fessential services.
