OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO called to give
OL,4,Cevidence to MPs after Kent supply
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThe Committee says it expects to
OL,8,Fconsider the company's written
OL,9,Fresponse to the Chair's questions
OL,10,Fabout planning, resilience, capacity
OL,11,Fand communications.
OL,13,FSEW says the taps will be back to
OL,14,Fnormal in Tunbridge Wells by Friday
OL,15,F(12 December) and the precautionary
OL,16,Fboil notice will be lifted by the end
OL,17,Fof the week, if everything goes to
OL,18,Fplan.
