OL,3,CSouth East Water CEO called to give
OL,4,Cevidence to MPs after Kent supply
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FThey say supply has returned to all
OL,8,Faffected customers, and no bacteria
OL,9,Fhad been detected in the water.
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat MP Mike Martin said
OL,12,Fthat the situation had been "a total
OL,13,Ffailure of leadership" and called for
OL,14,FMr Hinton to resign.
